## GitHub Actions Runner Environment
## Secrets injected by Ansible from Bitwarden at deploy time.

## GitHub App auth (auto-discovers installation, no INSTALLATION_ID needed)
APP_ID=ANSIBLE_WILL_REPLACE_THIS
APP_PRIVATE_KEY=ANSIBLE_WILL_REPLACE_THIS

## Runner config
RUNNER_SCOPE=repo
EPHEMERAL=true
RUNNER_WORKDIR=/_work
RANDOM_RUNNER_SUFFIX=false
